title: Lucid Motors Steps Up Production as Supply Chain Problems Ease
description: The maker of electric luxury sedans said it made more than 7,000 cars in 2022, achieving a scaled-down target.

title: How Arizona Is Positioning Itself for $52 Billion to the Chips Industry
